**Occult Wolf** | Werewolf Group | Transformation
__Basics__
The Occult Wolf is a cult player who was turned into a wolfpack member.
__Details__
If any of the members of the cult group are turned into a wolf somehow they will instead be turned into an Occult Wolf.
The Occult Wolf is a member of the cult still meaning they can vote on the cult's kill polls.
The Occult Wolf is strongly disguised as their previous role.

__Simplified__
The Occult Wolf is a cult player who was turned into a wolfpack member.
